<div class="rte">
<a name="health"></a>
<h2>Health</h2>
<p><span class="xlarge-text">Concordia‚¨"s deeply innovative approach to health research, education, policy and technology focuses on the full continuum of issues and interventions.</span></p>
<p><span class="xlarge-text">This comprehensive and integrated research capacity, which runs the gamut from engineering to social sciences to arts and humanities, supports transdisciplinary responses to health challenges across six themes:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span class="xlarge-text">Biomedical Fundamentals,</span></li>
<lihttp://www.concordia.ca/next-gen/cities.html,</span></li>
<li><span class="xlarge-text">Health and Technology,</span></li>
<li><span class="xlarge-text">Health Policy and Governance,</span></li>
<li><span class="xlarge-text">Health and Wellbeing, and</span></li>
<li><span class="xlarge-text">Health Interventions.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span class="section-header"><br>
Health Initiative</span></p>
<p><span class="xlarge-text">The Health Initiative at Concordia supports faculty members as they work at the intersections of disciplines to collectively focus on a range of health-related approaches across the lifespan, and with the involvement of citizens, community groups, policy-makers and other stakeholders.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span class="xlarge-text">Join the Initiative to expand and enhance your research. Connect with <a adhocenable="false" href="http://www.concordia.ca/directories.html?f=search&fname=shazma&lname=abdulla">Shazma Abdulla</a>, Lead, Health Initiatives and Special Projects, for support with developing proposals towards non-traditional agencies, as well as health-related research engagement opportunities.</span></p>

</div></div>


<div class="button parbase section">

<a style="margin-bottom: 10px;" class="btn btn-ghost-dark btn-block " href="../health-initiative.html" target="_self"><span>Discover our research</span></a></div>
</div>



</div>
</div>


</div><div class="parsys_column cq-colctrl-lt0-c1 span6 no-gutter ">

<div class="hero parbase section"><div class="hero-container picturefill-container square " style="background-color: #000; background-position: center top; "><div data-picture><div data-src="/content/concordia/en/research/spotlights/jcr:content/content-main/box_1251206495/box-parsys/hero/adaptiveimage.img.768.medium.jpg/1542317696021.jpg" data-media="(max-width: 768px)"></div><div data-src="/content/concordia/en/research/spotlights/jcr:content/content-main/box_1251206495/box-parsys/hero/adaptiveimage.img.full.medium.jpg/1542317696021.jpg" data-media="(min-width: 769px)"></div></div><div class="overlay  " style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0, 0), rgba(0,0,0, 0));"></div><div class="hero-text yposition-desktop-40 yposithttp://www.concordia.ca/directories.html?f=search&fname=shazma&lname=abdulla<div class="text-area " style="width:100%;"><h1 class="medium-large text-color-FFFFFF"> </h1><h2 class="text-color-FFFFFF"></h2></div></div></div></div>


